  "intent_precise": "Protein Array: Using reagent reservoir (reservoir, slot 3), Teleshake with slides mounted (labware, slot 4), sample plate (pcr_plate, slot 10). (1) Transfer 150\u00b5L from set_a 1 to destination. (2) Pause: Shake for 30 minutes at room temperature on TeleShake before resuming. (3) Incubate for 5 minutes. (4) Transfer 100\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (5) Pause: pause_str (6) Incubate for 5 minutes. (7) Incubate for 5 minutes. (8) Incubate for 5 minutes. (9) Pause: Prepare 1:1000 secondary antibody solution (2 ml total volume per slide) in PBST and place in channel 2 of the 12-channel reagent reservoir (slot 3). (10) Pause: Incubate the samples by gentle agitation for 1 hour using TeleShake before resuming. (11) Incubate for 5 minutes. (12) Incubate for 5 minutes.",
